products.title: Long Cuff Ring Shirt
products.description: fit & detail It is made with a trendy overfit, and is a comfortable and practical product with a dropped shoulder line and relaxed sleeve length. The wide collar design does not make the neckline look cramped, and you can feel the effect of making your face look smaller. With a loose fit and length that covers the hips, it covers the body shape and at the same time creates a soft fit to add a feminine mood. The wide cuffs are the point. Fold the cuffs in half or straighten them out and give them a point with a ring to create a variety of styles. With a basic shirt design, it can be worn alone or layered with various items. It is a long cuff ring shirt made by Looknon, which is highly recommended for daily use.
